{
  "stem": "18572.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were not with the partisans, because partisans wouldn't take children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But there were groups of partisans and there were groups of Jews in hiding.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "During one of the raids, they killed both my uncles.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I guess we were in hiding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But another one of those really vivid memories that I have is another time, when these Ukrainians came-- and for whatever reason, I was sitting, like, under a bush.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think part of it was because I couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were questioning my mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were talking to some of the other people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Later, she told me that she-- that they said that they were communist partisans and they were there to help us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But she recognized one of the people as being Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So she wanted to get away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So she somehow told them there were other people and that she wanted to go get them and come back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I remember sitting under the bush and knowing that this was dangerous.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it's one of those, like, pictures that you get in your head.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it also occurred when-- I mentioned to you Judith Kastenberg had interviewed me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as a child-- for her to jar my memory, she-- she said, look below.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And what I remembered of the Germans were the boots.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And what I remembered here in this forest were the boots-- you know, those black boots.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I knew that we were in danger.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was sitting under this bush and saying to myself, I'm just gonna crawl away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And nobody is going to know I'm here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at the same time-- it's amazing to me now, but I remember the feelings, and at the same time saying to myself, how can I crawl away and leave my mother?",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
